@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((0.34 / (v1 + 0.85 + v2 + 0.85)))
    v0 = wp.cos(v1)
    tmp = v1
    tmp = 0.17
    v1 = wp.exp(((v2 + 0.08 / v2 + 0.89) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.17)))
    tmp = ((0.91 - (v2 + 0.41 / v0 + 0.15)) / wp.cos(tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
